text: The Pashto Wikipedia () is the Pashto language version of Wikipedia. It started in 2003. As of August 2014, it has over 5,000 articles, over 46,299, over 24,039 registered users and over 1,595 files. == References == == Other websites == * Pashto Wikipedia's main page Category:Wikipedias Category:Websites established in 2003
